repower-rare-trip-sensitive-test-site-2024-08-20/</link><description>周二，台湾在访问台湾东南海岸偏远地区的一个敏感试验场时，在记者面前发射了一组地对空导弹，展示了其导弹火力。</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 02:23:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-shows-off-missile-firepower-rare-trip-sensitive-test-site-2024-08-20/</guid></item><item><title>美联储鸽派押注亚洲股市触及一个月高点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-08-20/</link><description>亚洲股市周二触及一个月高点，追随华尔街反弹，因市场预期美联储可能会在本周晚些时候进一步暗示即将降息。</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 01:58:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-08-20/</guid></item><item><title>降息押注导致美元在近7个月低点附近波动，鲍威尔讲话成为焦点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-seven-month-low-rate-cut-bets-powell-speech-focus-2024-08-20/</link><description>由于押注美国央行将从下个月开始降息，美元周二在七个月低点附近波动，交易员等待周五美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔的评论。</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 01:14:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-seven-month-low-rate-cut-bets-powell-speech-focus-2024-08-20/</guid></item><item><title>正如预期，中国维持主要贷款基准不变</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-leaves-key-lending-benchmarks-unchanged-expected-2024-08-20/</link><description>中国周二将基准贷款利率维持在月度固定利率不变，符合市场预期。</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 01:08:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-leaves-key-lending-benchmarks-unchanged-expected-2024-08-20/</guid></item><item><title>央视称前中国足球高管因受贿被判入狱</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/former-chinese-football-association-director-handed-7-years-jail-bribery-cctv-2024-08-20/</link><description>据中央电视台周二报道，中国足协原竞赛部主任黄松​​因受贿罪被判处有期徒刑七年。</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 01:04:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/former-chinese-football-association-director-handed-7-years-jail-bribery-cctv-2024-08-20/</guid></ite