bDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 19:00:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-widely-expected-keep-lending-benchmark-lprs-unchanged-aug-2024-08-19/</guid></item><item><title>资金撤退，实物买家赢得铜市争夺战</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/physical-buyers-win-battle-copper-market-funds-retreat-2024-08-19/</link><description>逃离铜市场的投资者可能会在数月内处于观望状态，这为预计主要消费国中国和其他地区的需求在未来几个月内恶化并对价格造成压力的实体参与者留下了空间。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 11:02:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/physical-buyers-win-battle-copper-market-funds-retreat-2024-08-19/</guid></item><item><title>早间出价：随着杰克逊霍尔的临近，美元出现下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-2024-08-19/</link><description>塞缪尔·因迪克 (Samuel Indyk) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 10:18:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-2024-08-19/</guid></item></channel></rss>